OL,3,CFamilies devastated over Trusts
OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,FFamilies have been left devastated and
OL,7,Fstruggling to provide round-the-clock
OL,8,Fcare to loved ones with severe
OL,9,Fdisabilities after health trusts
OL,10,Fblocked unqualified carers from
OL,11,Fproviding nursing tasks they have been
OL,12,Fdoing for years.
OL,14,FThe families have said the Trusts have
OL,15,Ftold them that carers paid through the
OL,16,FDirect Payments system can no longer
OL,17,Fcarry out or be trained to carry out
OL,18,Fthe nursing tasks.
