OL,3,CFamilies devastated over Trusts
OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,FFour of the main Health Trusts are
OL,7,Freviewing the legislation and policies
OL,8,Faround Direct Payments on what those
OL,9,Fcarers can and can't do. The
OL,10,FDepartment of Health says it has not
OL,11,Fcommissioned a formal review.
OL,13,FHowever, there has been a warning that
OL,14,Funless the trusts allow carers to
OL,15,Fcarry out nursing tasks, families will
OL,16,Fnot be able to cope and some people
OL,17,Fwill end up in full-time care.
OL,19,FThe Centre for Independent Living says
OL,20,Fthere needs to be a change in the law.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
