OL,3,CFamilies devastated over Trusts
OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,FDeena Nimick, Policy and Campaign
OL,7,FManager at the organisation, said:
OL,8,F"More and more people are coming
OL,9,Fforward with this same problem.
OL,11,F"We don't understand why it's
OL,12,Fhappening. But the legislation needs
OL,13,Fto change.
OL,15,F"We need either emergency legislation
OL,16,For we need new legislation, in the
OL,17,Fsame way that other parts of the UK
OL,18,Fhave."
