OL,3,CFamilies devastated over Trusts
OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,FMum Tracey had an assistant paid for
OL,7,Fby Direct Payments to help with that
OL,8,Fcare, however, the Northern Trust has
OL,9,Ftold her it will not allow the
OL,10,Fassistant to carry out that element of
OL,11,Fher care.
OL,13,FShe told UTV the change means she can
OL,14,Fnot leave the house now under the new
OL,15,Farrangements.
OL,17,FShe said: "There wouldn't even be an
OL,18,Fhour between when she gets up in the
OL,19,Fmorning and she goes to bed at night
OL,20,Fwhen I can go out."
