OL,3,CFamilies devastated over Trusts
OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Northern Trust
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are in the process of
OL,8,Freviewing Direct Payments in relation
OL,9,Fto the relevant legislation around
OL,10,Fhealth care tasks that can be
OL,11,Fadministered under Direct Payment
OL,12,Farrangements. We are committed to
OL,13,Fproviding the highest standards of
OL,14,Fcare and will continue to liaise with
OL,15,FEllie's family to ensure Ellie
OL,16,Freceives the care she needs."
OL,18,FMichaela Hollywood requires 24-hour
OL,19,Fcare.
