OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,FHer Direct Payments are used to employ
OL,7,Fa team of assistants and like Ellie,
OL,8,Fshe too is fed and medicated through a
OL,9,Ftube.
OL,11,FBut Michaela said the South Eastern
OL,12,FTrust told her they do not have any
OL,13,Ftrained carer assistants to administer
OL,14,Fher medication - so she has to rely on
OL,15,Fher mother who has arthritis.
OL,17,FMichaela said: "Her hands are so sore
OL,18,Ffrom through the years of having to do
OL,19,Fit... my mummy is 72."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
