OL,3,CFamilies devastated over Trusts
OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,FThe South Eastern Trust said it could
OL,7,Fnot comment on individual cases.
OL,9,F"We are currently working in
OL,10,Fpartnership with our regional
OL,11,Fcolleagues to agree a position on the
OL,12,Ftraining and delegation of nursing
OL,13,Ftasks to unqualified social care staff.
OL,15,F"We completely understand the
OL,16,Fchallenges this may cause families,
OL,17,Fhowever if nursing tasks are required,
OL,18,Ffamily members are educated and
OL,19,Fsupported by the Trust to provide this
OL,20,Flevel of care."
