OL,6,FThe Department of Health added:
OL,7,F"Regionally, direct payments are
OL,8,Foffered by Health and Social Care
OL,9,FTrusts in lieu of a social care
OL,10,Fpackage to enable a more personalised
OL,11,Fmethod of care provision and to allow
OL,12,Fpeople to live as independently as
OL,13,Fpossible at home.
OL,15,F"Policy on direct payments is
OL,16,Fspecifically designed to be person
OL,17,Fcentred. The needs of service users
OL,18,Fare individually assessed and a care
OL,19,Fplan is then drawn up by the Trust.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
