OL,4,Cnursing care block for carers
OL,6,F"Individual needs may change over time
OL,7,Fand these needs will also be different
OL,8,Fto others receiving a direct payment.
OL,10,F"In specific, individual
OL,11,Fcircumstances, if there is a
OL,12,Fparticular complex need to be met
OL,13,Fwhich falls outside of the routine
OL,14,Fscope of a social care service, then a
OL,15,Fformal delegation process may need to
OL,16,Fbe considered by the Trust.
