OL,6,F"There is no formal review underway.
OL,7,FHowever, health and social care Trust
OL,8,Fteams working in this service area
OL,9,Fregularly engage with teams from other
OL,10,FTrusts. This is common practice for
OL,11,Fmany services across the HSC.
OL,13,F"Training arrangements for PAs
OL,14,F(carers) are an operational matter for
OL,15,FTrusts."
